snippet.textDisplay:
Well nothing against these amazing artists but having listened to couple of songs from coke studio india this I now understand why coke studio Pakistan is considered better than any other coke studio. They are way ahead of CS India in terms of content , music arrangement, the set designs, the vocals, the subject of their music and the entire thought process behind creation. There is just so much depth and variety in their creations. Their seems a purpose behind their music which is why the music seems to be having a dialogue with listeners posing some serious questions and evoking range of emotions.
Sorry but I just don't see that magic happening here and by the way this is for the 1st time I have tuned into CS India. I listened to few songs from CS Bangla and didn't find it any better.
I apologize to all those who feel hurt by my remarks but that's what I felt as a music lover
